  "prompt": "What are some best songs to listen to?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" songs can be quite subjective, as it often depends on personal taste, mood, and the genres you enjoy. However, here's a diverse list of highly acclaimed and popular songs across various genres and eras that you might enjoy:\n\n---\n\n### **Classic Hits**\n1. **\"Bohemian Rhapsody\"** \u2013 Queen\n2. **\"Imagine\"** \u2013 John Lennon\n3. **\"Hotel California\"** \u2013 Eagles\n4. **\"Stairway to Heaven\"** \u2013 Led Zeppelin\n5. **\"Hey Jude\"** \u2013 The Beatles\n\n### **Pop**\n1. **\"Blinding Lights\"** \u2013 The Weeknd\n2. **\"Shape of You\"** \u2013 Ed Sheeran\n3. **\"Bad Guy\"** \u2013 Billie Eilish\n4. **\"Uptown Funk\"** \u2013 Mark Ronson ft. Bruno Mars\n5. **\"Rolling in the Deep\"** \u2013 Adele\n\n### **Rock**\n1. **\"Smells Like Teen Spirit\"** \u2013 Nirvana\n2. **\"Sweet Child O' Mine\"** \u2013 Guns N' Roses\n3. **\"Under the Bridge\"** \u2013 Red Hot Chili Peppers\n4. **\"Enter Sandman\"** \u2013 Metallica\n5. **\"Livin' on a Prayer\"** \u2013 Bon Jovi\n\n### **Hip-Hop/Rap**\n1. **\"Sicko Mode\"** \u2013 Travis Scott\n2. **\"God's Plan\"** \u2013 Drake\n3. **\"HUMBLE.\"** \u2013 Kendrick Lamar\n4. **\"Old Town Road\"** \u2013 Lil Nas X ft. Billy Ray Cyrus\n5. **\"Lose Yourself\"** \u2013 Eminem\n\n### **R&B/Soul**\n1. **\"Crazy in Love\"** \u2013 Beyonc\u00e9 ft. Jay-Z\n2. **\"Thinking Out Loud\"** \u2013 Ed Sheeran\n3. **\"Adorn\"** \u2013 Miguel\n4. **\"All of Me\"** \u2013 John Legend\n5. **\"Say You Won't Let Go\"** \u2013 James Arthur\n\n### **EDM/Electronic**\n1. **\"Titanium\"** \u2013 David Guetta ft. Sia\n2. **\"Levels\"** \u2013 Avicii\n3. **\"Don't You Worry Child\"** \u2013 Swedish House Mafia\n4. **\"Closer\"** \u2013 The Chainsmokers ft. Halsey\n5. **\"Wake Me Up\"** \u2013 Avicii\n\n### **Indie/Alternative**\n1. **\"Take Me Out\"** \u2013 Franz Ferdinand\n2. **\"Dog Days Are Over\"** \u2013 Florence + The Machine\n3. **\"Electric Feel\"** \u2013 MGMT\n4. **\"Somebody Else\"** \u2013 The 1975\n5. **\"Ho Hey\"** \u2013 The Lumineers\n\n### **Latin**\n1. **\"Despacito\"** \u2013 Luis Fonsi ft. Daddy Yankee\n2. **\"Bailando\"** \u2013 Enrique Iglesias ft. Descemer Bueno, Gente de Zona\n3. **\"Tusa\"** \u2013 Karol G & Nicki Minaj\n4. **\"Mi Gente\"** \u2013 J Balvin, Willy William\n5. **\"Havana\"** \u2013 Camila Cabello ft. Young Thug\n\n---\n\n### **Recent Favorites (2020s)**\n1. **\"Levitating\"** \u2013 Dua Lipa ft. DaBaby\n2. **\"Good 4 U\"** \u2013 Olivia Rodrigo\n3. **\"Montero (Call Me By Your Name)\"** \u2013 Lil Nas X\n4. **\"Peaches\"** \u2013 Justin Bieber ft. Daniel Caesar & Giveon\n5. **\"Save Your Tears\"** \u2013 The Weeknd\n\n---\n\n### **Timeless Ballads**\n1. **\"Someone Like You\"** \u2013 Adele\n2. **\"Fix You\"** \u2013 Coldplay\n3. **\"Yesterday\"** \u2013 The Beatles\n4. **\"Unchained Melody\"** \u2013 The Righteous Brothers\n5. **\"Stay With Me\"** \u2013 Sam Smith\n\n---\n\n### **Feel-Good Tunes**\n1. **\"Happy\"** \u2013 Pharrell Williams\n2. **\"Can't Stop the Feeling!\"** \u2013 Justin Timberlake\n3. **\"Wake Me Up Before You Go-Go\"** \u2013 Wham!\n4. **\"September\"** \u2013 Earth, Wind & Fire\n5. **\"Dancing Queen\"** \u2013 ABBA\n\n---\n\nThese suggestions cover a range of genres and styles, so there's likely something you'll enjoy. If you have specific preferences\u2014like a particular genre, mood, or era\u2014feel free to let me know, and I can provide more tailored recommendations!",
